ointment/\' target=\'_blank\'>帮助部分</a>访问这些文章。','Button Text'=>'按钮文字','Open link in new tab'=>'在新标签页打开链接','Error 404'=>'404错误','Author Archive'=>'作者归档','Posted on'=>'发布于','You must be <a href="%s">logged in</a> to post a comment.'=>'要发表评论，您必须先<a href="%s">登录</a>。','Name'=>'名称','Leave your message'=>'留下您的信息','CREATE TRUSTWORTHY WEBSITES'=>'创建可信赖的网站','A website exists for one and ONLY one reason:'=>'网站存在的唯一理由：','To bring you more business.'=>'为您引来更多的生意。','Think of your website as a hardworking salesman who works 24/7 and never asks for a raise!'=>'请考虑您的网站是一个很勤奋的推销员工作24 / 7，从不要求加薪！','In this email course I deliver 4 highly actionable tips on how you can build a website which is trustworthy and which, in turn, brings more business to you.'=>'在这个电子邮件课程，我提供了4个高度可操作的技巧如何建立一个值得信赖的网站，为您引来更多的业务。','JOIN COURSE'=>'参与课程','Customize'=>'自定义','Features'=>'特色','Frontpage Sections'=>'首页区域','You will find a number of sections on the front page.'=>'您会在首页找到很多区域。','Page Templates Support'=>'页面模板支持','Various Page Templates included in the Appointment Premium Theme'=>'Appointment Premium主题中包含各种页面模板','Mobile Friendly'=>'适用于移动端','Responsive layout in all devices'=>'响应布局。 适用于各种设备。','Contact Form Support'=>'联系标支持','SEO Friendly URL'=>'SEO友好URL','This feature allows you to rename the custom post type slug names in the URL.'=>'此功能允许您重命名URL中的自定义帖子类型别名。','Multiple Color Schemes'=>'多色彩方案','Enjoy using the 13 preset color schemes. You can also create custom skins without adding any code.'=>'享受13种预设色彩方案。您还可以在不添加任何代码的情况下创建自定义外皮。','Google Maps'=>'Google地图','Display your Shop and Business location on your website using Google Maps.'=>'在您的站点上使用Google Maps显示您商店和商业的地点。','Portfolio'=>'作品集','Present your project/portfolio collection with 2 column, 3 column and 4 column layouts. You can also display your project/portfolio by category.'=>'用2列、3列或4列布局呈现您的项目/作品集集合。您还可以按类别显示项目/作品集。','About Us Page'=>'关于我们页面','Show team members, your clients and custom content added in the WordPress editor.'=>'显示在WordPress编辑器中添加的团队